TAKE 3 GROUPS (DEV, TEST, PROD)
EACH GROUP 2 NODES = TOTAL = 6 NODES & 1 MAIN NODE

CREATE A PLAYBOOK FOLDER

5 TASKS  -- > ROLES

ROLE-1: CREATE 5 USERS ON ALL GROUPS
ROLE-2: INSTALL HTTPD & RESTART ON TEST GROUP
ROLE-3: DEPLOYMENT ON DEV & PROD SERVERS (GITHUB -- > PULL FROM PLAYBOOK) ALL GROUPS
ROLE-4: INSTALL DOCKER ON REDHAT BY USING CONDITIONS DEV GROUP
ROLE-5: INSTALL NUMPY & PANDAS ON ALL GROUPS
ROLE-6: INSTALL JENKINS IN PROD SERVERS


=========================================================================
- hosts: all
  become: yes
  tasks:
    - name: install httpd
      command: yum install httpd -y

    - name: start service
      command: systemctl start httpd

    - name: copying the code
      copy:
        src: "index.html"
        dest: "/var/www/html/"
